Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:02.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:32.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We switch to summer uniforms today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like Konata will probably show up in her winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least one person in our class will forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's one in this house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.63,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,257)}All Kinds\Nof\NPeople
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:54.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:58.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to sign up for the TV drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda wanted the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An apron from Apron of Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:04.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot because you don't have enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:08.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:12.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More like I've been busy with student council stuff and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:13.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are just excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on the same level as\Nsomeone who only even thinks about having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the way you put it really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you win a drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:29.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a loveless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:32.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you jot down the usual stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you put on yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff that'll help me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good handwriting is a fundamental must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:47.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to design a postcard that just begs to be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:48.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a fluorescent marker to draw a border around the postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:03:00.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you add a picture related to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't draw very well though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just send in as many entries as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can probably handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many you send...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:19.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...write each one out without using a printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And send out a hundred each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that cost a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting for something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That calls for passion and guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't it be cheaper just to buy it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some things in this world can't be bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fit a hundred postcards in a mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't send them all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but a few here and a few there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And over the course of a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on who's running the drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sometimes you're better off without the tricky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes it's the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:02.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...glance through free newspapers and flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:12.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and look for drawings that\Nprobably aren't going to attract many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have a high chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's the love in that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, for twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't look anything like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause we're two-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One-egg twins look exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's more like comparing sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but two-egg twins can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty different in appearance and personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa is laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Kagami is pretty psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had the same hairstyles with the same ribbons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might end up looking the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kona-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:50.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami could never be the cutesy type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:52.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me with your weird fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:58.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when they're raised separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:06.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they end up having similar lifestyles and significant others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes they end up marrying another pair of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when one of them is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the other one can sense it from a completely different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all kinds of mysterious phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So can't you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Abracadabra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You read way too much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with ManaKana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,ManaKana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they have a few differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mana is the careful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Kana is the optimistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:37.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently they sound a little different when they sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,ManaKana thought they were two-egg twins for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they recently learned that they were actually one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The definitions for one-egg and two-egg twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...have changed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that you two could be one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your identical traits would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You both like sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:03.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:10.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,White maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The same colors as your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:22.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All this talk about eggs and black\Nand white cookies has made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was talking about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suffocating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got on and I've already broken a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't turned on the air conditioning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:53.39,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(211,259)\frz10.882\fs10}Soujiro Izumi\NKonata
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:53.39,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(271,401)\frz11.215pos(274,426)\fs10}After a long courtship,\Nwe, Kiyotaka Narumi\Nand Yui Kobayakawa,\Nwill be tying the knot\Non June **.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybug Samba, punk version.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my cousins is getting married this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she'll be a June bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:10.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wet and gloomy season supposedly signify happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does getting married in June make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The name June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is generally said to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...derived from the name of the Roman goddess, Juno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In Greek mythology...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Juno is known as Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the goddess of marriage and fertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why those who get married\Nin Hera's month, the month of June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...are said to receive her protection and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't Hera Zeus's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this image of Hera being extremely jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm not feeling this happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:48.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather wear a dress or a kimono for your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would wear a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also go with a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a kimono would also be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna wear both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have miniskirts and really colorful dresses these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A miniskirt wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd look really cute with lots of frills on the hem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Angel Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:22.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:25.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair makes you look more like Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So a yellow top and miniskirt it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably look good in a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dress is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the person you're getting married to is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a rich lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One has lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the ability to cast Beho*mi and l***zun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But as far as feelings are concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the true love type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd go for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No comeback, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a question about a game I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:07.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Kagaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more fun when you figure it out yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you understand that you should do things yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll do your own homework from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the detectives in manga and TV shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:28.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...run into an awful lot of murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like in Conan or Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There wouldn't be a story otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they just solve normal cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like travel around Japan in search of missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tailing people would translate well into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With plenty of thrill and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:47.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could also conduct investigations into unfaithful wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or look for pets that ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But would that be fun to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cases in real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't really use any brilliant tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the ones you find in manga and TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabricated fingerprints that can't be\Ndetected through a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff that's a step ahead of forensic labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:17.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything too good might lead to copycats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or be too sensitive for broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, or that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:28.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The really hard cases end without\Nanyone realizing they happened or go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:28.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be wrong in so many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hate how it's been constantly raining the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used to like rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You get soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you can't hang clothes out to dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I've never really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you like rain, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:55.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because baseball games would be\Ncanceled and I'd get to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds just like something you would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a lot more dome stadiums now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.89,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(331,452)\fs18\frz345.239}CROMARTIE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:06.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:13.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You often see idiots and geniuses\Ngoing to the same school in anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease that immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, neener-neener!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that actually kinda strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in some recent anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:27.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the teacher looks the same age as the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(283,28)\frz10.617}YOUTH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(489,45)\frz354.758}HI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,108)\frz345.118}IT'S\NBACKWARDS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(79,265)\frz1.941}BACKWARDS IS\NTHE GREATEST ECSTASY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,213)\frz349.443}LUCKY STAR DASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(562,423)\frz345.389}WHAT'S IMPORTANT IS\NWHAT'S INSIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(59,395)\frz348.673}AGE MEANS NOTHING\NIN THE FACE OF LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.21,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(61,442)\frz5.278}WRYYYYY~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ta*****na-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's always been interested in watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the gap between physical age and mental age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, wouldn't a student who's\Nreally different from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...be the real mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:49.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree one hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't know how you got into this school, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at putting stuff off till the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you didn't study until the night before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:06.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean she really did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't have pulled it off in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm impressed that you actually kept studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a quiz game come out for DS or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad set some conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A D-rank would mean a Pippin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A C-rank would mean a 3DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A B-rank would mean a PS2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Papa Izumi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really know how to deal with your daughter, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the real mystery how Tsukasa's in the same school as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.16,ls_alternative_2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come back in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it without even blinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.85,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I can't beat her at fighting games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}She's spent way more time than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge to me a different game if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A quiz game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Konata in a game of knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she memorized the question order?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.22,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\i1}Her memory's incredible when it comes to gaming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a really easy party game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know all the games I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could probably beat me at that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It just stunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've barely eaten any snacks, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you wolf them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no real reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieting for summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you have anyone to show your swimsuit off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:43.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:45.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you guys born on Tanabata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your birthday soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:50.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen's right before the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the year before a critical year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unlucky things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As our birthday approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm getting worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I bought a bunch of wards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and power stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop buying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have wards against rage at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wards against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wards against rage, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:25.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We ensure safe pregnancy and protect\Nyou from traffic accidents at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that your birthday is Ponytail Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:37.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why July 7th?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Vega from the Tanabata legend had a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Japan Ponytail Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:54.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they give an award every year to a\Ncelebrity who they think would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:00.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a feeling that anyone would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair's the shortest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's barely a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a little ponytail's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours also looks good, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could go with that on an everyday basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:21.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:29.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami's is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:31.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll undo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All manly like a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drunks often wear ties around their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just when the guy loosens the tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tries to pull it off over his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it gets stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:56.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a lot weirder that they're always carrying a takeout box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeout box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing Kato-chan from the Drifters carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunks these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:09.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty much always have a tie around\Ntheir head and a takeout box in their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Vega and Altair meet this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine. Shine. Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope those rage wards of yours can deliver a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're giving away all varieties of QUO cards at Comp Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always collecting QUO cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do you ever use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why spend the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural to want any item...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...related to a series you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As a fan. As a collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:40.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you're never gonna use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take good care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:49.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really pisses me off when I see someone use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to use these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Much less auction them off or sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Using them makes you a surefire failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a fan and as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't say anything when you're so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I at least need three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One for preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep it in a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one to take out occasionally to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the last one for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:21.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you always want two or three of something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:24.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:27.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:28.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd expect Tsukasa to be popular with guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've never heard anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:40.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's a little plain and doesn't really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because she's got a scary sister guarding her like a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I'm really plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or it's more that Kona-chan and Yuki-chan are really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki knows all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Has a good figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:57.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hates the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}You kinda derailed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I haven't heard anything about Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because she's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that everyone's afraid to approach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and really good at helping others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a lot of guys ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she turns them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Turns them down, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:18.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she doesn't realize that they're asking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan can be a little clueless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so an indirect approach might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the guys in your class are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't a single one of them have the guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to confess his passionate feelings to Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough maniacs in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's type is usually a bigger hit with maniacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniacs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:49.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:54.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:02.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going on with the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that person was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:14.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody at least does it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what you call an element of turning people on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:33.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:46.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's another whoo-whoo happy episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:53.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:54.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:57.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us have now done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three times after today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about it, Shiraishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:10.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like Shiraishi-san hasn't opened up to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like we're sitting further apart than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they mean by emotional distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:23.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got something the fans will love today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing our first\Nintroduction for a member of the regular cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Da! Da-da-dum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be introducing Miyuki Takara-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The class representative, well-mannered, kn—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:42.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:43.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in both literary and culinary arts. A perfect person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Miyuki-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so wonderful, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, there's her glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she's pretty as a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With those looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd expect her to be hard to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's actually a friendly person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd talk that much on the radio show...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop talking when it's about Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki Takara-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With large breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And various other turn-ons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.23,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Akira-sama, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Isn't she so lucky to be a pretty character?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The maniacs loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.80,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Uh, maniacs is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:24.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's maniacs you want, I'm a huge hit with those lolicons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:39.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Send us any questions or comments about the show please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's she really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:51.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she like smoke a pack at a time backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No worry of that. She isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A unique song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear a song that normal people can enjoy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the next one, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:08.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it from the intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not another weird song, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was this song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:17.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:18.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:21.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from FMP. FMP.
